{"tid":146461,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"<Last Order> 同<New Order>係咪唯一Wyman同夕爺互相呼聲的歌曲?","createTime":"2017-03-07T06:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T11:58:18.000Z","uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e42cb03fe0f2cbc4629f40a4c31cb6eb7115420a","tid":146461,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅 <br />\n<br />\nLAST ORDER<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SD80XgYR-fE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSD80XgYR-fE&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=be3d550a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SD80XgYR-fE</a><br />\n<br />\n作詞：黃偉文<br />\n作曲：Eric Kwok<br />\n編曲：Eric Kwok<br />\n<br />\n沒關係　真的沒關係　我也許　早就該回去<br />\n再一杯　我告訴自己　到此為止　乾了不再續<br />\n麻煩你　加冰威士忌　對不起　來個DOUBLE的<br />\n喝到這裡　終於夠勇氣　說一個經歷<br />\n<br />\n那晚下雨　在這店裡　也放著這首曲　有個男子　搭上一個女子<br />\n反正失戀　他當然不介意有段艷遇　只是回到　他的家裡<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=aad45506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n十幾坪　家徒四壁　一聲不響　那女的　掉頭離去<br />\n就像　三個小時前　未婚妻　初次到來　嫌棄的樣子<br />\n【就像　我的未婚妻　對不起　好像說成是我的樣子　我是沒關係】<br />\n<br />\n沒關係　真的沒關係　一晚上　就失戀兩次<br />\n那男子　還不懂懷疑　到底自己是否沒出息<br />\n不客氣　別給我ICE TEA 客人們不是我嚇跑的<br />\n別看著我　這個不過是　我朋友的經歷<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅 <br />\n<br />\nNEW ORDER<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p7JmIoUdT-o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp7JmIoUdT-o&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=df223e34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p7JmIoUdT-o</a><br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕<br />\n作曲：Eric Kwok<br />\n編曲：Eric Kwok<br />\n監製：Eric Kwok<br />\n<br />\n等一等　先生你要的　可不可　給你換雪碧<br />\n我與你　其實未相識　不過怕你喝得這麼激<br />\n請想想　她不愛你的　為何還　枉花這氣力<br />\n出不出色　給拋棄過的　也替你不值<br />\n<br />\n＊容我直言　這酒吧中　天天企到三點<br />\n不想吸煙　捱完二手香煙<br />\n每晚打烊　獨自回家睡眠　從來未變<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=aad45506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n我這六年　一天一天　聽酒客　自語自言<br />\n怨氣震天　即使我　越聽越厭<br />\n卻要笑著　前來逐一敷衍　隨和像我　也真的少見<br />\n(我卻笑著　前來賺多點錢　來年讓我　去開間花店)＊<br />\n<br />\n想開心　不必做富翁　她當天　聽了沒法懂<br />\n更怪我　仍舊是打工　不愛與我吃這西北風<br />\n當天起　加班再見工　我信我　這雙手很有用<br />\n這一杯酒　都花過苦工　給你免費享用<br />\nREPEAT(＊)<br />\n<br />\n讓我過新一天"},{"pid":"df5c7070bd274bd71955abb6873d63c5a155dfb8","tid":146461,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"兩首Eason 都演繹得好好"},{"pid":"bd11cea6945af1269e57b3a10eed6b3837f39b92","tid":146461,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"互相呼應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea49d2fe2358a7aa279a7e83d8ca1b8877c7952","tid":146461,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"NEW ORDER 太夾硬"},{"pid":"f974903785cacdcd951373156cdc6cb910277f6d","tid":146461,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>NEW ORDER 太夾硬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少有林夕會玩cross over<br />\n<br />\n我都覺last order 正d"},{"pid":"b6ce5bc7376307f1fe0cc266d3de3557f01c8e0c","tid":146461,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:58:18.000Z","msg":"兩首歌係呼應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> last order 醫生唱到好攰，好灰嘅感覺；反而New order係旁觀者，聽落去稍為精神少少。<br />\n<br />\n利申：自以為識"}]}